{"id":601601,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/【敏感词库】习狗、开倒车/","date":"2018-12-14T07:19:49Z","modified":"2018-12-14T16:34:15Z","title":"【敏感词库】习狗、开倒车","content":"<p>12月11日，有微博网友爆料：微博发布包含“习狗”的文字（例：作为实习狗加班好累）会导致触发“抱歉，因此内容中存在违反相关法律法规或《微博社区公约》的信息，无法进行当前的操作。”而无法发布，显然微博已将此词列为发布禁词。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-601602\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/image.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/image.png 675w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/image-169x300.png 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/image-576x1024.png 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>此外，中国数字时代11月29日曾报道，B站将“<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91b%E7%AB%99%E5%BC%80%E5%80%92%E8%BD%A6%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%BA%B7%E7%BA%B7%E7%A6%81%E8%AF%84/\">开倒车</a>”、“包子”等词列为了“禁评”触发词，只要是标题或描述中含有这些词汇一律禁止评论。</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91b%E7%AB%99%E5%BC%80%E5%80%92%E8%BD%A6%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%BA%B7%E7%BA%B7%E7%A6%81%E8%AF%84/\">【立此存照】B站“开倒车”视频纷纷“禁评”</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"【立此存照】新浪微博敏感词：“包子” = 零阅读\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e6%96%b0%e6%b5%aa%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%ef%bc%9a%e5%8c%85%e5%ad%90-%e9%9b%b6%e9%98%85%e8%af%bb/\">【立此存照】新浪微博敏感词：“包子” = 零阅读</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"【敏感词库】修宪相关禁词2：“梦回大清”“迪士尼”“撸起袖子”等\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e4%bf%ae%e5%ae%aa%e7%9b%b8%e5%85%b3%e7%a6%81%e5%8f%91%e8%af%8d2%ef%bc%9a%e6%a2%a6%e5%9b%9e%e5%a4%a7%e6%b8%85%e8%bf%aa/\">【敏感词库】修宪相关禁词2：“梦回大清”“迪士尼”“撸起袖子”等</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"【敏感词库】菜谱敏感词之“洗净平”\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e3%80%91%e8%8f%9c%e8%b0%b1%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e4%b9%8b%e6%b4%97%e5%87%80%e5%b9%b3/\">【敏感词库】菜谱敏感词之“洗净平”</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,16848],"tags":[37219,13222,9249,31267,37220,9283,8859]}